        https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=56618

        * UIProcess/Plugins/PluginProcessProxy.cpp:
        (WebKit::PluginProcessProxy::PluginProcessProxy):
        Initialize m_fullscreenWindowIsShowing.

